        <title>ubuntu 22.04 server安装Nvidia驱动</title>
        <link>https://ynhugo.github.io/p/ubuntu-22.04-server%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85nvidia%E9%A9%B1%E5%8A%A8/</link>
